{"title":"海南诗抄","authors":["柯原"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海南诗抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘红豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山红豆熟了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮晶晶宝石挂树梢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山红豆熟了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万绿丛中飘火苗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠竹编花篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金线缠剪刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘好似蜂采蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪下相思知多少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问声红豆寄哪个？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘不语先微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采红豆不为寄相思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻人不兴唱老调。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满把红豆寄北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为表姑娘志气高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学红豆千日红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不学杜鹃花易雕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰寨歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家窗户朝海开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前房后椰树多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草席平铺晒红鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹笼高挂养鹦哥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寨门四季鲜花红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰寨主人最好客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝迎车队带露来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮送征帆披纱过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腰挂砍刀攀椰树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵笑声云中落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采来椰果大如斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情意千金买不着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰汁清凉加蔗糖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满斟美酒任你喝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰肉滑腻如凝脂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细嚼来滋味多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天黑请吃竹筒饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜深点串海棠果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉椰胡，奏鼻箫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合唱一曲椰寨歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国江山美如画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处人心红似火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人一夕椰寨宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三载难忘我的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采木棉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月风吹木棉树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一树彩霞红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月风吹木棉树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵棉桃满枝悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社书记带队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭开雾帐进深山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊起宿鸟绕枝飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇落露珠一串串。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子身轻如燕上高枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳里洒下阵阵棉桃雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘手巧挥弯刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月牙一闪，流星落竹篮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风吹来银絮飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只只蝴蝶舞蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们欢叫来捕蝶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声没入花丛间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采呀采木棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵白云飞下山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装满车，装满船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺织厂姊妹笑开颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采呀采木棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纺成那金线和银线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织一幅筒裙彩虹色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣一幅锦绣五指山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月飞鱼汛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月飞鱼汛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆樯集海面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三角艇小巧，大拖风宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔轮上风动红旗火焰翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里南海成闹市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又好似黎家歌舞三月三。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日东升，金光染渔帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺号悠扬，汽笛声喧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船头击水浪花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手搭凉棚四处看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥见鱼群回游处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水波里飞出双双燕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚风起，船上万灯明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星光灯影溶成一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打渔人来到银河里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琼楼玉树任流连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞鱼群逐穴投进网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆的鱼儿飞上船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆挂新月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银装满船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水波粼粼渔港近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡高唱起炊烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，岸边一片彩霞红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满街凤凰树开花迎归帆。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}